com.wizturn.sdk.peripheral

Class Peripheral

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.Observable
      • com.wizturn.sdk.peripheral.Peripheral

  • public class Peripheral
extends java.util.Observable
    Defines a bluetooth device which acts as peripheral role(e.g. beacon).
